nepali-calendar (1.1.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Window-level GestureDrag with CAPTURE phase fixes swipe on Wayland.
  * Week view redesigned: self-contained day cards with day name inside each card.
  * Removed stale swipe callbacks from CalendarView and WeekView.

